  (text "UI (docs/09 s.3): TCA9535 (0x20) - port0 PRESENT, port1 panel keys, 16x 10K\npull-ups (part has none). Display: generic ILI9341+XPT2046 14-pin module on\n3V3 VCC; backlight switched HIGH-side (50-120mA, beyond a GPIO). EC11 with RC\nconditioning (bench). LEDs sink like the module board; buzzer low-side + flyback." (at 25.4 27.94 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 12a35a3b-e746-4a6f-8435-3a97aec73803))
